description: Removes the log-level override, if any, for a specific resource ID and resource type. It can be used for a wireless device, a wireless gateway, or a FUOTA task.

parameters.name: ResourceIdentifier
parameters.description: The unique identifier of the resource, which can be the wireless gateway ID, the wireless device ID, or the FUOTA task ID.

parameters.name: ResourceType
parameters.description: The type of resource, which can be WirelessDevice, WirelessGateway, or FuotaTask.
